{"tid":128254,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲廉航 究竟帶到幾多野上機？","createTime":"2017-02-20T16:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T12:04:13.000Z","uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb09e946c489fa450cfff465579fc07b39379721","tid":128254,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:07:27.000Z","msg":"真係諗到頭都大 <br />\n暑假要去europe 1個月exchange <br />\n想staybehind 2 個星期<br />\n呢兩個星期會搭飛機去唔同國家<br />\n想問下大家 連登達人 <br />\n如果我帶一個中型backpack <br />\n再加個20 吋 gip 仔上機 <br />\n會唔會過唔到ryanair 果d 條款？<br />\n聽講check 得幾嚴 但總之塞到入個鐵箱就ok <br />\n有無巴打有意見！？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfefa13373b58e138911ef3270d01c2e623d246","tid":128254,"uid":30272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"唔可以backpack加gip<br />\nBackpack要收得落gip<br />\n<br />\n加上size上官網寫好清楚 無得走雞"},{"pid":"a8482432a5715d8f86a9801af803d2d57f6e0ce0","tid":128254,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:19:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔可以backpack加gip<br />\nBackpack要收得落gip<br />\n<br />\n加上size上官網寫好清楚 無得走雞</blockquote><br />\n嘩 真係好撚癲"},{"pid":"70e0cbfb0d81ef2df6fffcc1fa226b6dc02335be","tid":128254,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔可以backpack加gip<br />\nBackpack要收得落gip<br />\n<br />\n加上size上官網寫好清楚 無得走雞</blockquote><br />\n嘩 真係好撚癲</blockquote><br />\nOne cabin bag weighing up to 10 kg with maximum dimensions of 55cm x 40cm x 20cm, plus 1 small bag up to 35 x 20 x 20 cms may be carried per passenger*. 上網係咁"},{"pid":"a3c69f3c631952078402827afb2846aa51e3eb83","tid":128254,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔可以backpack加gip<br />\nBackpack要收得落gip<br />\n<br />\n加上size上官網寫好清楚 無得走雞</blockquote><br />\n你講起又記得幾年前係咁 朋友要夾硬塞落去"},{"pid":"ecff4204c1b3e0af66b0736eb9972bf494e8a149","tid":128254,"uid":79185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:31:05.000Z","msg":"個中型backpack唔過佢個personal bag limit就無問題啦<br />\n個人覺得ryanair唔係好嚴，搭過幾次都未試過要塞行李落鐵架<br />\n同埋好多人拎多過兩件cabin bag都冇俾人捉"},{"pid":"9a912b6aa0e2b078436894f14c3ce0b258f39ef6","tid":128254,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"間間唔同,<br />\nRyanair 最濕鳩<br />\nEasy jet 好d"},{"pid":"a6c37b45ab913c9f734c3ec675677c8bea9b819b","tid":128254,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個中型backpack唔過佢個personal bag limit就無問題啦<br />\n個人覺得ryanair唔係好嚴，搭過幾次都未試過要塞行李落鐵架<br />\n同埋好多人拎多過兩件cabin bag都冇俾人捉</blockquote><br />\n真係唔同人唔同"},{"pid":"d02cdeed21522dd089e83899f9df815e0c7e6384","tid":128254,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間間唔同,<br />\nRyanair 最濕鳩<br />\nEasy jet 好d</blockquote><br />\n有無巴打試過預先寄個luggage 返香港先？"},{"pid":"e0394f442abfd7845036c845996fae2990b8319e","tid":128254,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"ryanair已經好hea，一個手提喼加背囊都得，我試過一次比佢塞鐵架check岩岩好就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />wizzair個d先濕鳩"},{"pid":"200fe780487987763d7673d4b2c4f0e30908b026","tid":128254,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ryanair已經好hea，一個手提喼加背囊都得，我試過一次比佢塞鐵架check岩岩好就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />wizzair個d先濕鳩</blockquote><br />\n如果我帶細gip 仔 加個55L 既backpack 會唔會Gg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c789142cf18c434c120ac92476f56fb9463089c0","tid":128254,"uid":82960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>間間唔同,<br />\nRyanair 最濕鳩<br />\nEasy jet 好d</blockquote><br />\n有無巴打試過預先寄個luggage 返香港先？</blockquote><br />\n同問,我都想知,去exchange半年,但之後想去其他地方玩,但拎住哂咁多行李好麻煩! 我想寄啲野番黎香港先,尤其冬天厚衫個啲,但唔知可以點搞"},{"pid":"354683ee22c87146045ca40562e75dda501824b0","tid":128254,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:07:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ryanair已經好hea，一個手提喼加背囊都得，我試過一次比佢塞鐵架check岩岩好就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />wizzair個d先濕鳩</blockquote><br />\n如果我帶細gip 仔 加個55L 既backpack 會唔會Gg <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個backpack應該唔得"},{"pid":"ef0eac6e944ec63bb0e7c09e24a1b382a101461f","tid":128254,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:08:47.000Z","msg":"人地寫明哂有咩限制，有幾癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286372b571e91e288ca675355f254f5d5963783f","tid":128254,"uid":33674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:09:57.000Z","msg":"巴打會唔會考慮火車/巴士？之前個fd去exchange都係咁"},{"pid":"820327489bc23f501bd20a0de6d9e716b6083ccf","tid":128254,"uid":79185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>間間唔同,<br />\nRyanair 最濕鳩<br />\nEasy jet 好d</blockquote><br />\n有無巴打試過預先寄個luggage 返香港先？</blockquote><br />\n同問,我都想知,去exchange半年,但之後想去其他地方玩,但拎住哂咁多行李好麻煩! 我想寄啲野番黎香港先,尤其冬天厚衫個啲,但唔知可以點搞</blockquote><br />\n你最後唔會返exchange嗰度走? 如果返，睇下可唔可以擺住係人地度先啦<br />\n無謂特登俾多幾舊水郵費"},{"pid":"48579abf8b35e24e8e226852831a904460a9f0be","tid":128254,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:52:20.000Z","msg":"咁平有得你飛仲話人癲<br />\n你咁把炮就自己包架私人機啦<br />\n大鄉里到攞住自己把尺去量度外面世事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d01a9e33679aa2b01206a7e7b95bd006447c10a","tid":128254,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T19:34:28.000Z","msg":"1. 寄左行李返香港先<br />\n2. 如果係返exchange個到走，擺係fd到。個陣我擺係landlord到，走再攞返"},{"pid":"3f9a0a30d47a009f5fb713d905ef5ed5c5dceb5b","tid":128254,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T20:38:56.000Z","msg":"連手袋仔都要塞入喼入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67c9125156df44c28f4bbe0da92625ef9147516","tid":128254,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T20:42:45.000Z","msg":"一個出街backpack走天涯表示行李上ryanair冇難度<br />\n<br />\n驚行李size太大可以用好薄好薄既行李袋<br />\n好過用喼<br />\n喼好易塞唔落<br />\n<br />\n一開始去旅行又行李袋又中型出街backpack<br />\n一開始好驚佢捉行李<br />\n上機嗰下會塞晒backpack d野同backpack入個行李袋到<br />\n後來見ryanair冇點捉 試過一兩次中型backpack加行李袋上機都冇問題 （可能少客）<br />\n（但之後真係見佢上機前一個一個check<br />\n塞唔落好似要即磅）<br />\n<br />\n但再之後旅行得多 d行李愈黎愈少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩廿幾日都係一個出街backpack<br />\n仲要廿幾日玩既地方溫差有三十度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c524e6c95a53fd8e3dcdf7f992f1ad37c56ba3d","tid":128254,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T20:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>間間唔同,<br />\nRyanair 最濕鳩<br />\nEasy jet 好d</blockquote><br />\n有無巴打試過預先寄個luggage 返香港先？</blockquote><br />\n同問,我都想知,去exchange半年,但之後想去其他地方玩,但拎住哂咁多行李好麻煩! 我想寄啲野番黎香港先,尤其冬天厚衫個啲,但唔知可以點搞</blockquote><br />\n千祈唔好拎咁多行李去旅行<br />\n淨係搬行李都搬撚死你<br />\n歐洲太多要行樓梯既地方<br />\n寧願洗少少錢store行李<br />\n寄行李好似幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b79bc35942a04fe1566b94e1c3d081bcce9daa0","tid":128254,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T23:07:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"699204d9507a805815fbaf67060f1543061d5403","tid":128254,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T01:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>間間唔同,<br />\nRyanair 最濕鳩<br />\nEasy jet 好d</blockquote><br />\n有無巴打試過預先寄個luggage 返香港先？</blockquote><br />\n同問,我都想知,去exchange半年,但之後想去其他地方玩,但拎住哂咁多行李好麻煩! 我想寄啲野番黎香港先,尤其冬天厚衫個啲,但唔知可以點搞</blockquote><br />\n千祈唔好拎咁多行李去旅行<br />\n淨係搬行李都搬撚死你<br />\n歐洲太多要行樓梯既地方<br />\n寧願洗少少錢store行李<br />\n寄行李好似幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼要一千hkd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c8f785afb83ec6fac0d2ed7e0a90bb88fbdee1","tid":128254,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T01:35:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁平有得你飛仲話人癲<br />\n你咁把炮就自己包架私人機啦<br />\n大鄉里到攞住自己把尺去量度外面世事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 55 大財團走狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcaeb242d6d6dabfdb2718148219f1ea5217ee6","tid":128254,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T01:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 寄左行李返香港先<br />\n2. 如果係返exchange個到走，擺係fd到。個陣我擺係landlord到，走再攞返</blockquote><br />\n以為自己好醒 簡左open jaw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}